00:23:19,895 --> 00:23:28,096
[SPEAKER_06]: How these are structured, again, reinforces the idea that there's quite a bit of self-governance provided to the commission.

248
00:23:28,677 --> 00:23:37,138
[SPEAKER_06]: And it's stipulated here that there are certain things that we need to work for, work towards and support.

249
00:23:38,378 --> 00:23:48,380
[SPEAKER_06]: But really how we do that is left up to the commission to decide and really to what scope and to what scale and to understand

250
00:23:49,180 --> 00:23:50,121
[SPEAKER_06]: what is reasonable.

251
00:23:50,141 --> 00:23:56,846
[SPEAKER_06]: I don't think anybody on the board expects that we can fully eliminate all unlawful discrimination.

252
00:23:57,106 --> 00:24:02,110
[SPEAKER_06]: It would be outstanding, but that's a bit of a heavy lift for our group here.

253
00:24:03,211 --> 00:24:17,442
[SPEAKER_06]: So thinking about what is being asked, what the functions and powers are, what is reasonable to be done, what is ideal, and how best to get those wheels moving and keep them moving so that

