00:27:31,114 --> 00:27:36,277
[SPEAKER_06]: I know those are some topics that have come up before, so interested to pause and hear if there's any additional thoughts.

278
00:27:41,064 --> 00:27:42,465
[SPEAKER_05]: All right.

