00:27:47,728 --> 00:27:57,434
[SPEAKER_06]: The city solicitor, which I know is a bit of an issue right now for the city of Medford, but when we have a city solicitor, they are to act as counsel for the commission.

281
00:27:58,255 --> 00:28:02,077
[SPEAKER_06]: And as far as the definitions go, I link back to the full text.

