00:30:12,021 --> 00:30:15,662
[SPEAKER_06]: I already brought up the questions around the quorum regulations.

302
00:30:17,482 --> 00:30:31,786
[SPEAKER_06]: And if we should use the requirement to provide hard deliverables as a case to receive funding from the city, we're not gonna hand in a handwritten report on, you know, lined paper ripped out of a notebook.

303
00:30:32,066 --> 00:30:37,188
[SPEAKER_06]: I think the imperative to hand over something that looks professional could possibly be used as a reason

304
00:30:38,028 --> 00:30:39,449
[SPEAKER_06]: get some funding from the city.

305
00:30:39,809 --> 00:30:47,916
[SPEAKER_06]: That could be maybe the one-off grant that enables us to do the work that would enable us to seek further funding in the future, just a thought.

