00:33:53,045 --> 00:34:16,231
[SPEAKER_09]: Okay, so having stared at this ordinance on and off for more than 10 years, and having done two, at least two or three edit, complete thorough edits of it, I wanna point out that, and this is something that the Safe Medford Committee, it became abundantly clear to us.

