341
00:35:16,422 --> 00:35:17,782
[SPEAKER_09]: So I wanted to clarify that.

342
00:35:19,123 --> 00:35:35,412
[SPEAKER_09]: The other thing is, if you look at the document closely, that every list, for example, as we see here, a list of the reasons why someone might be discriminated against, every list in the document differs.

343
00:35:36,957 --> 00:35:39,679
[SPEAKER_09]: So that's something else to be kept in mind.

344
00:35:40,419 --> 00:35:48,984
[SPEAKER_09]: But basically they're almost all in the housing discrimination section, but they're not all, because there's one right at the beginning.

345
00:35:49,845 --> 00:36:02,112
