346
00:36:02,932 --> 00:36:06,635
[SPEAKER_09]: You know, put that at the beginning of the, of the ordinance.

347
00:36:07,215 --> 00:36:09,457
[SPEAKER_09]: So I just want to clarify a couple other points.

348
00:36:11,118 --> 00:36:18,583
[SPEAKER_09]: One in terms of subcommittees, subcommittees are generally speaking subject to the open meeting law and Munir is an expert on that.

