[SPEAKER_09]: The city developed a process that specifically

355
00:37:00,301 --> 00:37:18,284
[SPEAKER_09]: puts that responsibility within the, the HR department of the city, or maybe it's actually maybe Francis has that responsibility but Neil Osborne had that responsibility and reporting directly to the mayor on grievances.

